text: Peder Falstad (February 7, 1894 - February 11, 1965) was an American ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1932 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1894 births Category:1965 deaths Category:American male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the United States Category:Ski jumpers at the 1932 Winter Olympics Category:People from Snåsa
